{"tid":57593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【直擊起飛前】三對三貼身服侍 李嘉欣大陣仗去北海道","createTime":"2016-12-28T06:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-10T18:18:52.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2afa8018940a8762e9a1f10d344b379c070a7e94","tid":57593,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"早個星期五（16日），李嘉欣趁囝囝Jayden Max學校放長假就一家三口去北海道過白色聖誕。難得一家人去旅行，嘉欣隆重其事！ 一家三口，兩個工人姐姐，再加埋助手，三對三，貼身服待。 <br />\n<br />\n排隊入閘嘅時候，囝囝心急想打尖，嘉欣即刻捉住囝囝，教佢要守秩序，小JM都聽教，乖乖地跟住媽咪。 <br />\n<br />\n勁鍾意日本嘅嘉欣，上個月先同老公去過日本慶祝結婚8週年。今次諗住開開心心帶埋仔仔遊日本，可惜呢次日本行激嬲咗嘉欣。去旅行最緊要開心，不過咁樣滯留新千歲機場3日，今日凌晨3時多才回港，出發前幾興奮都係假。 <br />\n<br />\n不過最緊要係依家全部人順利返到香港，囝囝又覺得開心就夠啦。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/145751_1e4c8fa92b6b3430109ae95e80ecc029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F145751_1e4c8fa92b6b3430109ae95e80ecc029.jpg&h=7878de24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">嘉欣講述滯留日本情況。(唐家輝攝)</span>"},{"pid":"e03070904b5d47096a04d24748503a0276956092","tid":57593,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"7607fb3d81c334f3c3a166230d484ffe7d4b4f41","tid":57593,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></span>"},{"pid":"06e2ccf3bfa338e5e3abbf6df54efe05400fddac","tid":57593,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span></span>"},{"pid":"4b77b48827da6271afb78004a90c1bee3d55cf22","tid":57593,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T23:56:47.000Z","msg":"成篇文邊度大陣仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日借啲意攻擊大美人李嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03eeb9e93502723a24b7b860dfd6b571c062fde9","tid":57593,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成篇文邊度大陣仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日借啲意攻擊大美人李嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大美人李嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6aa1ce1da28ac18d9ce1f1198b9e04c215aac1b","tid":57593,"uid":20979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"唔滯留去北海道黎把撚呀?"},{"pid":"7a6a7a08a3282387c1be1fc93b05a366158ff189","tid":57593,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}